The Sofitel is very comfortable, and although a larger luxury hotel it retains it dutch feeling.	If you want a cute canal house - this is not for you but if you want luxury, amenities, excellent staff and a great location, then look at the Sofitel.	It is just a rather clumsy attempt by a rather mediocre chain, Sofitel, of trying to move into the luxury travel section, when they should stay doing what they do well, 3* - 4* hotels.	Overall, this is a five star hotel that doesn't compromise and certainly lives up to the expectations of the Sofitel brand.